  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study was to investigate the changes on heart rate variability, exercise
      capacity, activities of daily living, and quality of life after aerobic exercise training in
      cardiac transplant recipients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
